  "metadata": {
    "role": "article",
    "roleHeading": "Article",
    "title": "Localizing a Subscription Feed"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can provide localizations of your subscription content by linking to a supplemental",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "JSON object that maps locale IDs to locale-specific feeds.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Create-the-Localization-Mapping-in-JSON",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Create the Localization Mapping in JSON",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Each localization of your subscription’s content requires its own entry in the supplemental",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "JSON object. You create the mapping from a locale ID—a standard format described",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "in ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/MacOSX/Conceptual/BPInternational/LanguageandLocaleIDs/LanguageandLocaleIDs.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/10000171i-CH15-SW9",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": "—to",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the localized feed URL by pairing the two for that locale. You use the locale ID",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "as the key and the localized feed URL as the value for each key-value pair in the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "JSON object.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For example, you can supply the following locale JSON to support a feed that’s localized",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to contain English and French versions of a subscription’s content:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "{",
            "    \"en\": \"en-feed.json\",",
            "    \"fr\": \"fr-feed.json\"",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "javascript",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The locale ID for the French localization is ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "fr",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", and ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "fr-feed.json",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " contains French",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "metadata and the URL for the localized French playground books in the subscription.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Share-the-Localized-JSON-Objects-URL",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Share the Localized JSON Object’s URL",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Unlike feeds that aren’t localized, localized feeds download the supplemental JSON",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "object as an extra step to determine locale information before downloading your feed’s",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "content. As a result, you need to use the URL for the supplemental JSON object when",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "sharing your subscription.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "localizing-a-subscription-feed-1",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
